# UI Component & Design Guidelines

## General Principles
- **Identify existing component patterns before writing new code**
- **Prefer extending before creating new components**
- **Style using design tokens throughout:**
  - Do not use hardcoded colors/spacing
  - Place all styles in `src/styles`, not inline/inside components

## Component Structure
- **Where to put components:**
  - Design system & base: `src/components/ui/`
  - Layout: `src/components/layout/`
  - Features: `src/components/features/`

## Best Practices
- Prefer composition over custom variants
- Avoid duplicate style/logic, and do not create one-off variants
- Use purpose-driven naming for components/styles
- Use CSS Modules or styled-components where appropriate

